OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 3 May to Tue 12 May
OL,6,FDuring this period, conditions will
OL,7,Fprobably be fairly changeable, with
OL,8,Flow pressure systems in the vicinity
OL,9,Fof the UK. This means an increasing
OL,10,Fchance of showers or longer spells of
OL,11,Frain, along with some strong winds at
OL,12,Ftimes. However, dry interludes with
OL,13,Fspells of warm sunshine are still
OL,14,Flikely, with a risk of a few short
OL,15,Flived early morning fog patches,
OL,16,Fespecially around coasts. Temperatures
OL,17,Fare likely to be close to normal
OL,18,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
