OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1777385514
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 13 May to Wed 27 May
OL,6,FLow pressure systems are likely to
OL,7,Fdominate across the UK at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period. This means showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain are likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, heavy in places. There will,
OL,11,Fhowever, be some dry and warm
OL,12,Finterludes, although temperatures are
OL,13,Flikely to be close to normal overall.
OL,14,FLater in the month, more settled and
OL,15,Fdrier conditions may begin to develop,
OL,16,Fwith temperatures perhaps rising
OL,17,Fslightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
